title.narrative: Implementation of the Expanding Social Protection in Uganda Programme - Maxwell Stamp

description.narrative: This activity (Implementation of the Expanding Social Protection in Uganda Programme - Maxwell Stamp) is a component of Expanding Social protection in Uganda - Phase I reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £50,580,971. This component benefits Uganda, and works in the following sector(s): Social Protection. , with the following implementing partners: Crown Agents Bank, Crown Agents Limited, Maxwell Stamp PLC, THIRD PARTY MONIES. The start date is 01-04-2009 and the end date is 31-12-2017.
